
Week3 - Chapter  1- Quiz 1 


Q-1 When Python is running in the interactive mode and displaying the chevron prompt (>>>) - what question is Python asking you?


a)  What is your favourite color?


b) What Python statement would you like me to run?


c) What is the next machine language instruction to run?


d) What Python script would you like me to run?

answer- b) What Python statement would you like me to run?

